name: Lashes Lifting Silicone Shields Large 10pcs
description: Phi silicone shields come in three sizes in Small, Medium or Large, providing the clients a multiple option of potential looks that could be created, considering the length of their natural lashes and their preference and expectations of the final look from the lifting procedure. The smaller the shield used the greater and more dramatic the lift is to be achieved. The shields come in white color, providing your work precision even to the smallest details.
